name: mutpy
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "mutpy" %}
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/MutPy-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5a13ff28f30fb326cb6d9e9afe7431f36c156c00ff12ebf46f5fae1f7546bb3c

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 4
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - astmonkey >=0.2.2
    - jinja2 >=2.7.1
    - python >=3.6
    - pyyaml >=3.10
    - termcolor >=1.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - mutpy
    - mutpy.operators
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/mutpy/mutpy
  summary: Mutation testing tool for Python 3.x source code.
  license: Apache-2.0
  # License file manually packaged. Check status in future releases. See https://github.com/mutpy/mutpy/pull/74
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - thewchan
